name: Claro Escuro
description: This piece is parte of the #oBRjkt event. Just like caravaggio's baroque chiaroescuro, living in 2021's Brazil is an eternal contrast between the joys of living this amazing country and the darkness surround us like political extremism, uncontrolled pandemic, financial insecurity and police violence. Even though things may be dark right now, we must focus on the light, and the day that life will be able to bloom again.
